        <Parent_String>settlements by function: administrative [300120579], settlements by function [300008407], inhabited places [300008347], Settlements and Landscapes (hierarchy name) [300008346], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
